  "items": [
    {
      "name": "Let’s learn how to add two-digit numbers with carrying.",
      "actor": "Teacher",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Научимся складывать двузначные числа с переносом."
        }
      ],
      "actions": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Okay! What’s different?",
      "actor": "Student",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Хорошо! А что здесь по-другому?"
        }
      ],
      "actions": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Sometimes the ones go over 10, and we carry 1 to the tens.",
      "actor": "Teacher",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Иногда единицы дают больше 10, и мы переносим 1 в десятки."
        }
      ],
      "actions": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Try 47 + 36. Ones: 7 + 6 = 13. Keep 3, carry 1.",
      "actor": "Teacher",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Попробуем 47 + 36. Единицы: 7 + 6 = 13. Оставляем 3, переносим 1."
        }
      ],
      "actions": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Tens: 4 + 3 = 7, plus 1 = 8. So the answer is 83.",
      "actor": "Teacher",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Десятки: 4 + 3 = 7, плюс 1 = 8. Ответ — 83."
        }
      ],
      "actions": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Got it! 47 + 36 = 83.",
      "actor": "Student",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Понял! 47 + 36 = 83."
        }
      ],
      "actions": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Now try 58 + 27. Ones: 8 + 7 = 15. Keep 5, carry 1.",
      "actor": "Teacher",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Теперь попробуй 58 + 27. Единицы: 8 + 7 = 15. Оставляем 5, переносим 1."
        }
      ],
      "actions": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Tens: 5 + 2 = 7, plus 1 = 8. So, 85!",
      "actor": "Student",
      "dialogType": "Normal",
      "translates": [
        {
          "lang": "ru-RU",
          "name": "Десятки: 5 + 2 = 7, плюс 1 = 8. Значит, 85!"
        }
      ],
      "actions": []
    },
    {
